[1/19/2026]   
At the heart of the Service Value System (SVS) The service value chain is a flexible operating model for creating, delivering, and
continous improving of services.

[Six key activities] within the ITIL Service Value Chain

- Plan
- Improve
- Engage
- Design and transition
- Obtain/ Build
- Deliver and Support


Plan > improve > Engage > Design and transition > Obtain/Build > Deliver and Support.

